qol_worry_tab <- data %>% 
  filter(foc19_w2 != "Unworried" & !is.na(b_focqol)) %>% 
  mutate(b_focqol_cat == case_when(b_focqol > 6 ~ "Affected", 
                                   b_focqol < 7 ~ "Not affected", 
                                   TRUE ~ NA_character_)) %>% 
  group_by(b_focqol_cat) %>% 
  summarise(w_n = sum(weight, na.rm = T), 
            n = n()) %>% 
  mutate(perc = round(w_n / sum(.$w_n)*100,0))
